{"tid":2391951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣當局指繼續承認BNO為旅行證件","createTime":"2021-02-02T13:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T18:00:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2528a8f1848df83679511f86aef9e6178aa8fe19","tid":2391951,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T13:33:10.000Z","msg":"台灣當局表示，繼續承認英國國民(海外)護照、即BNO為旅行證件。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會及移民署回覆查詢時指，現行《香港澳門關係條例》及相關法規未變，仍可使用BNO申請入台證等，出入境證件到台灣；而已經憑BNO到台灣的港人，停留或居留台灣的權利未受影響。陸委會又呼籲，北京及香港當局依法保障港人自由權利。<br />\n<br />\n英國早前宣布，開放予合資格港人申請BNO簽證移民。在北京，外交部其後宣布不再承認BNO作為旅行證件及身份證明；特區政府亦指不能再用BNO在香港出入境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvb.com/local/60193ff434b031527e3d5b27/台灣當局指繼續承認BNO為旅行證件\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F60193ff434b031527e3d5b27%2F%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E6%8C%87%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8DBNO%E7%82%BA%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E8%AD%89%E4%BB%B6&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=9f190be4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvb.com/local/60193ff434b031527e3d5b27/台灣當局指繼續承認BNO為旅行證件</a>"},{"pid":"d52fb4175a08c9b61005b38875c931d52842b29d","tid":2391951,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:05:48.000Z","msg":"係唔係話長榮唔認？"},{"pid":"f8fc3d7c3369dba347679ca99c807bd0b659e714","tid":2391951,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf83fd34d204cb477519ed6d638b6782e466de2a","tid":2391951,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:11:41.000Z","msg":"特區呢"},{"pid":"5927021dd27d230362f273e4a2f241153698346f","tid":2391951,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d52fb4175a08c9b61005b38875c931d52842b29d","tid":239195